{"tid":200810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國外長指朝鮮半島一旦發生戰亂　無人能夠成為贏家","createTime":"2017-04-14T09:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T12:06:56.000Z","uid":41404,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"32d948afe571a3188a7c8acb099839d8886442fc","tid":200810,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T09:31:55.000Z","msg":"王毅指朝鮮半島一旦發生戰亂　無人能夠成為贏家<br />\n2017-04-14 HKT 17:22<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外長王毅表示，朝鮮半島的危險局面，值得高度關注和警惕。<br />\n<br />\n他說，一旦真的發生戰亂，結局只會是多輸，無人能夠成為贏家。<br />\n<br />\n王毅會見到訪的法國外長艾羅之後說，任何一方在朝鮮半島生戰生亂，都必須承擔歷史責任，付出相應代價。中方呼籲有關各方，不要再在口頭和行動上相互刺激和相互威脅，不要把事態推向不可收拾的地步。"},{"pid":"583cec66fe46b90d975c608803cb8a0a993b0aa7","tid":200810,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T09:35:44.000Z","msg":"中國或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9221a4fd873b7f54fdd1a42a787066cebc3bf006","tid":200810,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T09:37:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n到時美軍打埋佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"120b9fc2de168326d0f98c226e486892419c5e33","tid":200810,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T09:38:20.000Z","msg":"驚露底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5132bc211bd9d20aaec79767de723ab1e821e2","tid":200810,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T09:40:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中國又羸"},{"pid":"fc1d1151e510ce2d8e10ce8064e654eea91d0823","tid":200810,"uid":29874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T09:41:03.000Z","msg":"點解雜種去外訪時唔出聲嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d42501bbc10c52a935ccef23254ebd0052cdcd16","tid":200810,"uid":17684,"like